		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />They require javascript. Select the text you want to quote with the mouse, and click the button.<br /><br />For example, I can quote you like:<div class="quotetitle">tokumaru wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">they don't do anything</div><div class="quotetitle">tokumaru wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">but</div><div class="quotetitle">tokumaru wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">display</div><div class="quotetitle">tokumaru wrote:</div><div class="quotecontent">messages</div>

		

